item_equipment.item_description: A special ring issued to Supreme rank team members by Glorion, which is a special team of the Alliance.

A ring imbued with a mixture of joyful energy and sad energy. 
Right-click this ring to reset its stats and Potential. Can be reset 10 times weekly. Its remaining
reset count is reset every Monday. The best Resetting grade is Unique.

A ring with special powers made by the Alliance for the Tenebris Expedition, who are preparing to battle with the Black Mage.
Can only be used with Tenebris Expedition Ring Enhance Coupon
Potential and Additional Potential can be added.
No activation delay! Immediately increases your EXP rewards by 30%.
It contains the power of a terrible nightmare.
Can only be equipped in the Pocket slot.

item_equipment_preset_2.item_description:
A pair of wings said to have power over fate itself. 
You can get another one from Tengu if you lose it.

A special ability ring found in AWAKE Mountain.
Can only be used with AWAKE Ring Exclusive Enhancement Scroll.
Potential and Additional Potential can be added.

A ring full of vengeance against unknown targets. Resonates with Vengeance Stone to increase its power.
Potential and Additional Potential can be added.

A ring containing the cosmic order. Resonates with Cosmic Atom to increase its power.
Potential and Additional Potential can be added.
Increases the wearer"s Equipment drop rate by 20% by arousing greed.
